Deg useggas n [[1796]], Amsuji n Legniz [[Edward Jenner]] yessuddes-d (ihegga-d) [[tigezt]] mgal tazerzayt. Ma deg iseggasen n 40 n tsut yezrin tazerzayt tenger yakk deg [[Turuft|Uruppa]] d [[Tamrikt n Ugafa|Temrikt tagafant]], deg useggas n [[1967]] [[Tuddsa n Yeɣlanen Yeddukklen]] tessekr-d amezizzel i wakken ad titessenger ma deg useggas n [[1977]] iban-d igim aneggar di tmurt n [[Ṣumal]]. Deg useggas n [[1980]] Tuddsa n Yeɣlanen Yeddukklen tessilef-d d akken tessenger aṭṭan-a

== Asnirem n tigezt (ACRAṬ) ==
Deg iseggasen ineggura n [[Tasut tis 18|tsut tis 18]], Amsuji [[Edward Jenner]] iwula yerna yexdem tazrawt ɣef yiwet n teqcict isem-is Sarah Nilmes tetteẓẓeg tafunast tuɣit yakan tzerzayt yerna tettwaggeẓ mgal tazerzayt acku tella tuden s [[Tazerzayt n tfunasin|tzerzayt n tfunasin]]. Edward Jenner yufa-d d akken tinegwa d tirawin seg weglim n win yudnen s tzerzayt n tfunasin w ad t-yegzi i wakken ad tyaɣ waṭṭan-a d ayen ara ad s-d-yefken [[affal]] mgal n tzerzayt acku tazerzayt n tfunasin d win yettemcabin ar tzerzayt maca Kan ur telli ara d tamihant s waṭas 

== Anṭaṭ n waṭṭan ==
Tzerzayt d aṭṭan yetenṭaṭen s č meca ur yetenfufud ara s tazzla am waṭṭanen ivirsanen n iden, ahat aceku agajji niɣ asiwed yessutur asiweṭ yuddsen (ijehden) w yettili-d seld n tuffɣa n tuffɣiwin n weglim

== Anṭaṭ n yigim ==
Tazarzayt tettased seg yigim n ubirus n tzarzayt.

Igim yettaṭaḍ seg uselmeẓ n wezwu, akk daɣen si tquddirin n uxenziz n yimi, d uxenfuc akked tgersi.

Yettanṭaḍ seg umdan ɣer wayeḍ seg ubrid n taywalt udem ɣer wayeḍ i tallit tameqqṛant d umdan yeffudi ( مصاب) s umata ɣef ustum n 6 n yiḍaren ( 1,8 m ) i tallitin timeqranin akked umdan yeffudi 

Akken yezmer daɣen ad yenṭeḍ seg ubrid n taywalt tusridt neɣ s yimneggi n tfekka n ufuddi, akken yettenṭaḍ daɣen seg ubrid n ifecka n ufuddi, amedya: ictilen  الفراش،د, neɣ iceṭṭiḍen.

Drus anda tazarzayt tettenṭaḍ seg ubrid n ubirus i d-yettaddem waḍu deg wadagen ( imeḍqan ) umdilen, amedya: timaccinin, tikeryad... Atg, maca abirus yezmer ad yenṭeḍ di yakk tafekka akken yezmer ad yenṭeḍ seg ubrid n yibaɛɛac akked iɣersiwen, ma ur nerni ara asenfufed ( propager ) n waṭṭan.

Yettwaḥsab seg waddaden inaqqen seg ubrirus n tazarzayt.

Tḍarru-d tmettant ger wass wis mraw  ( 10 ) d wass mraw sḍis ( 16 ) n waṭṭan.

Taɣzint ( raison ) n tmettant  seg waṭṭan n tazarzayt ur d-ban ara.

